            . I am a Police-constable. I took the prisoner, and found on him a purse, three sovereigns, and five keys - I received this watch from the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-213-person1599">
                  GEORGE 
                  FINCH
               <interp inst="t18310630-213-person1599" type="surname" value="FINCH"></interp>
